Savor the Flavors of Ireland with Our Fun and Tasty Pub Grub! At our Irish Pub, we take pride in our warm and friendly hospitality. We strive to create a friendly and inclusive environment where everyone feels like part of the our family. Join us for an authentic Irish experience with a twist of fun in the heart of Hollywood, Florida. Sláinte! CONTACT US

About Us
Historic Downtown Hollywood is characterized by quaint sidewalk cafes, brick lined sidewalks, excellent fine dining restaurants and one ‘Brilliant Irish Pub!’
Mickey Byrne’s Irish Pub opened in November 2008 and our aim is to bring an authentic piece of modern Ireland to South Florida. (No kitschy Shamrocks and fiddles in glass cases here!)
Authentic Food (and more)
Of course like every great Irish Pub we offer an array of traditional Irish food dishes like an Irish Breakfast, Fish ‘N’ Chips, Shepherd’s Pie, and Bangers and Mash but we also have our famous hand-made Burgers (with our secret seasoning), vegetarian options and great wings!
Our Mission
Mickey Byrne’s Irish Pub is named after a famous Tipperary hurling legend so it is fitting that sports are a big part of our pub. We have all the big sporting events including the NFL ticket, MLB ticket, College Football, NBA, USA Men’s & Women’s Soccer, and Champions League Soccer on our massive big screen TVs and projectors.
MEET THE TEAM
BARTENDERS
And what’s an Irish pub without drinks? Mickey Byrne’s boasts an extensive selection of Irish whiskeys, beers, and cocktails, including the iconic Guinness stout, Irish coffees, and creative concoctions that are sure to impress. Our experienced bartenders are skilled at pouring the perfect pint and mixing up delicious cocktails to quench your thirst and keep the good times flowing.
